{
  "stem": "2916.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So we hid under the-- under the wagon, the three of us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And low flying planes were shooting at us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I saw it was an American plane.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The American Air Force was attacking us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There was a second attack.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then there was a third wave of attack again.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "These planes went away, and another one came.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And again, they sprayed machine gun fire into the train, under the train.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They even flew, flew low and sprayed the people among the trees who were-- there was a clearing there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the plane flew low, and I could see as they sprayed machine gun fire at the people, and they were dying as they were hiding between the trees.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then when the third wave was over, we were ordered back again into the trains.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We didn't understand what was going on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Many people were terribly wounded.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I'm describing it in my book.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "One of my friends' leg was torn off by the knee.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I grabbed the lower stump-- such an insane idea-- and I was holding it against her knee, and I said, Lilly, hold it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Hold it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I thought by holding it, it will grow back together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It was awful.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "One of my friends or I was shot at.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Awful injuries.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And the doors closed, and the train moved on again.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We didn't know why the Americans attacked us, but we thought maybe because they thought it was a military train.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But they saw the uniforms.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "They saw the prison uniforms, and they sprayed bullets, on them too as they were hiding, so I didn't-- we didn't know what was going on.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "By now, we are hungry and wounded and shivering from cold because the train was going into the mountains, the Bavarian mountains.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
